&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Physician Assistants&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
PAs may claim a maximum of&amp;nbsp;7.25&amp;nbsp;Category 1 credits for completing this activity. NCCPA accepts&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;AMA PRA Category 1 Credit&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;from organizations accredited by ACCME or a recognized state medical society.&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
