&lt;p&gt;This &lt;strong&gt;lecture&lt;/strong&gt; will cover the theory and many applications of filtering audio signals including graphic EQ&amp;#39;s, fast Fourier transform filtering, biquad filtering, resonant frequencies, and hardware filters. The lecture will contextualize these in artistic contexts.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The event&amp;nbsp;will be held in the Seminar Room of the &lt;a href="https://library.columbia.edu/libraries/music/directions.html" target="_blank"&gt;Music &amp;amp; Arts Library, 701 Dodge&lt;/a&gt;. Ask at the desk for directions to the Seminar Room.&lt;/p&gt;
