&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://anthropology.princeton.edu/people/ikaika-ramones" target="_blank"&gt;Ikaika Ramones&lt;/a&gt;, Assistant Professor of Anthropology at Princeton University&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://researchportalplus.anu.edu.au/en/persons/nayahamui-rooney" target="_blank"&gt;Nayahamui Rooney&lt;/a&gt;, Senior Lecturer in Culture, History, and Language at Australian National University&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.synchronicityearth.org/about-us/our-people/" target="_blank"&gt;Miriam Supuma&lt;/a&gt;, Programme Manager at Synchronicity Earth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Moderated by &lt;a href="https://anthropology.columbia.edu/content/paige-west" target="_blank"&gt;Paige West&lt;/a&gt;, Claire Tow Professor of Anthropology at Columbia University&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
